---
<section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary py-20 px-4 text-center relative overflow-hidden group">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-[2px]"></div>
    <div class="absolute -top-24 -left-24 w-96 h-96 bg-white/20 rounded-full blur-3xl group-hover:bg-white/30 transition-colors duration-700"></div>
    <div class="absolute -bottom-24 -right-24 w-96 h-96 bg-black/10 rounded-full blur-3xl group-hover:bg-black/20 transition-colors duration-700"></div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6 drop-shadow-md tracking-tight">Siap upgrade skill tahun ini?</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-100/90 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">
            Jangan lewatkan kesempatan emas ini. Daftar sekarang dan mulai perjalanan karir IT-mu bersama DBS Foundation dan Microsoft.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
             <a href="https://www.dicoding.com/codingcamp/registration?ref=4394693" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="relative overflow-hidden text-primary bg-white hover:bg-slate-50 focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-white/50 font-bold rounded-xl text-lg px-8 py-4 text-center transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 duration-300">
                <span class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-primary/5 to-transparent -translate-x-full hover:animate-[shimmer_1.5s_infinite]"></span>
                <span class="relative z-10">Daftar Coding Camp</span>
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.dicoding.com/elevate/registration?ref=4394693" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="relative overflow-hidden text-white border-2 border-white hover:bg-white focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-white/50 hover:text-purple-700 font-bold rounded-xl text-lg px-8 py-4 text-center transition-all shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 duration-300">
                <span class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/20 to-transparent -translate-x-full hover:animate-[shimmer_1.5s_infinite]"></span>
                <span class="relative z-10">Daftar METC</span>
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <p class="mt-8 text-sm font-medium text-white/80">
            Klik tombol &rarr; kamu akan diarahkan ke pendaftaran resmi Dicoding.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>
